title: We Took the Sexual Temperament Quiz with Dr. Emily Nagoski | Ear Biscuits Ep. 349
description:
Sextember continues! Did you know there’s no such thing as a sex drive? In this episode, Rhett and Link are joined by Dr. Emily Nagoski, author of Come As You Are, and they take her Sexual Temperament Assessment to see where they fall on the sexual spectrum. Plus - Link’s party glasses are back, and this time, Link has competition.

To learn more about the Dr. Nagoski’s work or to get a copy of her book, visit www.emilynagoski.com
